{"tid":148324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（新手）單車越來越慢，咩原因？","createTime":"2017-03-08T13:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T19:29:46.000Z","uid":13480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07bbe1ada41120acf29eb4f98560d9cfc2717420","tid":148324,"uid":13480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上年七月千幾蚊買左部trinx<br />\n<br />\n每個月踩三四次夜晚<br />\n<br />\n最近架車好似越來越慢<br />\n<br />\n個轆好緊<br />\n<br />\n好用力踩先得跑步咁快<br />\n<br />\n有機會係咩原因<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48afbfc6e0d7396dd9ff3eceaf092e9cf7633bf6","tid":148324,"uid":17110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"因為你越黎越快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94714aec6fd11f04a5ccdb6801930c26f5ac90cc","tid":148324,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"有冇同你呀爸講？"},{"pid":"7a8ccb6a814aa09b56fc58292c8d773559430012","tid":148324,"uid":13480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436c46d39b4a4827adb47293af0a985edb4628eb","tid":148324,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"你攰啦"},{"pid":"771dc9050a21da8fc5525f6c13027b1af7f4fe1f","tid":148324,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:15:02.000Z","msg":"日常保養"},{"pid":"472d673c21666e9f7a0a5e933788f7a726a48810","tid":148324,"uid":88236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:20:32.000Z","msg":"check下條呔夠唔夠氣"},{"pid":"f3bacb335f8ad34a627c900da521e35e7b6e0e5d","tid":148324,"uid":71020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"有冇拆過個碌？<br />\n可能條鈴high到個brake?"},{"pid":"309d548d8b0a81d3c132654c8a7ae3012ef0361c","tid":148324,"uid":38620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:23:59.000Z","msg":"可以試下抹下車，尤其係大餅同Bottom Bracket, 亦都可以試下落鏈油"},{"pid":"bb46fbd4b093d63c7ee749cbb38bb55e6b77f3d1","tid":148324,"uid":38620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:26:15.000Z","msg":"個轆緊亦都可能係因為有肴，或者掂住C夾"},{"pid":"949ae3f91ffb03dc5781675ebe8974015a2df3b4","tid":148324,"uid":73924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T19:29:46.000Z","msg":"Trinx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如換車啦<br />\n但如果你真係想整<br />\n<br />\nCheck 咗brake 有冇痴住條軨<br />\n冇就再檢查胎壓<br />\n胎壓冇問題就睇下條鏈有冇怪聲有冇生銹<br />\n鏈冇事就睇睇大餅同飛輪有冇生銹磨損嚴唔嚴重<br />\n都冇事就較最輕波抬起後轆攪下佢<br />\n覺得有阻力就空轉下後軨，阻力大就後軨有問題<br />\n冇問題就甩咗大餅位嘅鏈再轉下個大餅，有阻力即係BB有問題<br />\n冇就上返條鏈向後攪，阻力大一係就導輪有事一係就個free hub有事<br />\n都冇呢就拆前軨出黎轉下佢，唔順暢就係前軨有問題<br />\n<br />\n仲有多個意想不到嘅地方就係坐墊<br />\n如果滑低咗你<span style=\"color: red;\">係</span>會變慢<br />\n<br />\n如果check咗咁撚多野都冇問題<br />\n咁呢位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係你虧冇錯</span>"}]}